so we will finish up here. I want to ask you one

00:10:54.190 --> 00:10:57.840
more question, if like if someone is watching this. And you

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:59.820
know, there are like oh, you know, I wonder if I

00:10:59.820 --> 00:11:03.130
am color blind. Or maybe someone's recently found out they are,

00:11:03.130 --> 00:11:05.800
someone they know is. What advice would you give to somebody

00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:08.686
who may have recently find out that, you know, they are

00:11:08.686 --> 00:11:10.763
red green color blind? And of course there are other kinds

00:11:10.763 --> 00:11:13.570
